## âš™ï¸ Setup

1. **Create a `.env` file** in your working directory with the following variables:

```
GITHUB_USERNAME=your_github_username
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_token
SENDER_EMAIL=your_email@gmail.com
APP_PASSWORD=your_gmail_app_password
RECEIVER_EMAIL=recipient_email@gmail.com
```

> âš ï¸ Make sure to [generate a GitHub Personal Access Token (classic)](https://github.com/settings/tokens) with `repo` and `read:user` scopes.  
> âš ï¸ For Gmail, use an [App Password](https://support.google.com/mail/answer/185833?hl=en) (not your actual password).

